<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-04-17T21:29:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-04-17T21:29:00-05:00" n="608" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d608">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 337.11/445</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Gonzales</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-04-17T21:00:00-05:29">
                                    <hi rend="italic">April 17, 1917, 9 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Your April 16, 2 p.m. There are Government troops stationed at each one
                            these places except Canet. C. C. Reasoner, American, who recently went
                            to La Gloria to bring mother Habana, reports protection given by
                            Government to that section showed calm apprehension. Trains run through
                            Minas every day. I have not only asked for protection for alarmed
                            American colonies but where it was possible physically to get protection
                            have not rested till it was provided. Most of the robbery was before
                            communication could be established. Isolated houses will be in danger
                            while robber bands exist.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>